.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, azure, mauve, apricot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the person who likes mauve is the person driving the train##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who likes mauve##1
7. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Color         | ivory | apricot | mauve | azure |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

