.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, snowboarding, sailing, volleyball
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, skydiving, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Sport          | golf  | volleyball | sailing   | snowboarding     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking   | baking  | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | spy         | disaster  | mystery | thriller  |

