.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, pumpkin, peas, kiwi
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, french, nigerian, pakistani
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the nigerian##1
2. the pakistani is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
4. the person eating peas is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
6. the pakistani is the person drinking juice##1
7. the french is on the left of the pakistani##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | juice     | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Food   | kiwi  | cauliflower | peas       | pumpkin    |
| Nationality   | french   | pakistani | canadian    | nigerian |

