.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, reading, traveling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, metal, rock, trance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, amaryllis, azalea
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
| Flower         | daffodil   | poppy | amaryllis | azalea  |

